main event: Multiple observers spotted an unidentified object believed to be moving steadily about 100 yards away, estimated to be the size of an apple at arm's length, which was seen for about 5-10 minutes before disappearing.
interesting points: The object was reported to possibly ascend before it disappeared,Over 12 persons were contacted near the sighting location,The witnesses were noted to be reliable and credible,No physical evidence or photographs were found,An explosion involving a UFO was reported at around 32,000 feet near Parkston, South Dakota.
sighted object: Unidentified object believed to be vehicle-like
